## 📝 NOTES

### Why Native Android Over Flutter?
1. Better Mappls SDK integration (official native SDK)
2. More stable and mature SDK (v8.2.6)
3. Direct access to all Mappls features
4. Better performance for map rendering
5. Easier debugging and maintenance

### Why Web App Kept?
- Reference implementation for OSM/Overpass integration
- Demonstrates alternative approach without proprietary SDKs
- Can be used for testing/comparison
- Useful for areas where Mappls data is unavailable

### Mappls SDK Limitations
- Camera/hazard data requires enterprise license (₹50K+/year)
- Public SDK has limited POI density
- Built-in layers work but lack detail in some areas
- Route Safety Events API returns no data for most routes

